rows.label: qst201608_msg0001
rows.name:
Oh, you've come at a good
time, mo! Perfect timing, mo!

rows.label: qst201608_msg0003
rows.name:
The next concert has been decided,
mo. You'll be performing at the
Bajena Playhouse in Invidia, mo.

rows.label: qst201608_msg0005
rows.name:
Wow, that's amazing!
You did it, Nanakoori!

rows.label: qst201608_msg0006
rows.name:
Old man Cole's playhouse means it's
a bigger scale than last time, mo.

rows.label: qst201608_msg0008
rows.name:
You've been working hard in
your lessons. Your efforts have
been recognized, Nanakoori.

rows.label: qst201608_msg0012
rows.name:
Well then, Teetapz is
off to a meeting, mo!

rows.label: qst201608_msg0013
rows.name:
Nanakoori-san, let's make it
the best stage ever, mo!

rows.label: qst201608_msg0015
rows.name: You need to get ready, Nanakoori.

rows.label: qst201608_msg0016
rows.name:
Yes. It feels a bit daunting...
but I have to do it...

rows.label: qst201608_msg0017
rows.name:
I have something to discuss,
so please bring her here, mo.
